    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/6db5cd863fa20d02d2bc839e740a51af.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/6db5cd863fa20d02d2bc839e740a51af.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/6db5cd863fa20d02d2bc839e740a51af.mp4?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/f6576f01f513bcc429a7efb4007ded2e.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/f6576f01f513bcc429a7efb4007ded2e.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Button VR is a virtual reality game that challenges players to solve increasingly complex puzzles by pressing a button to progress to the next level as the primary mechanic for gameplay, which provides a unique and immersive experience for players.<br><br>As you advance through the levels, you will be faced with new challenges and obstacles to overcome, including intricate puzzles with quick thinking and precision. Each level is carefully crafted to provide an enjoyable sense of progression, with new content and mechanics introduced to keep you engaged and entertained.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/b4e1d74a3c3c76388c60860e88ca1900.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/b4e1d74a3c3c76388c60860e88ca1900.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/b4e1d74a3c3c76388c60860e88ca1900.mp4?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/e0eea9ca2bb1a92e9f8d86bac3c9aada.avif?t=1698187362\" width=608 height=132 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/d303c9e840d3afe9f2b61a96aa87a159.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/d303c9e840d3afe9f2b61a96aa87a159.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>The game's virtual reality component adds an extra layer of immersion to the gameplay, allowing players to fully immerse themselves in the game world and interact with objects in a more natural and intuitive way. The VR technology also allows for a greater degree of interactivity, with players able to use their hands and body movements to manipulate objects and solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/d7d1cfad9cb32b274b7bc9e8ced283b2.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/d7d1cfad9cb32b274b7bc9e8ced283b2.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/b324244eaf9a09734b5172ab8d8d395f.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/b324244eaf9a09734b5172ab8d8d395f.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/b324244eaf9a09734b5172ab8d8d395f.mp4?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>One of the key features of Button VR is the game's difficulty curve. As you progress through the levels, you are faced with increasingly challenging puzzles and obstacles that require more skill and expertise to overcome. This gradual increase in difficulty helps to keep the gameplay fresh and engaging, while also providing a sense of accomplishment and satisfaction for players who manage to complete the levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/92225d3e1fc24425a1212b4b740e58e2.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/92225d3e1fc24425a1212b4b740e58e2.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/92225d3e1fc24425a1212b4b740e58e2.mp4?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In terms of content, Button VR offers a range of different levels and puzzles to solve, each with their unique themes and challenges. Some levels may require players to navigate through a maze of obstacles, while others may involve complex logic puzzles that require careful analysis and critical thinking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/166c217e4528c8d05fe4abb3b4678296.poster.avif?t=1698187362\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221150/extras/166c217e4528c8d05fe4abb3b4678296.webm?t=1698187362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Overall, Button VR is an innovative and immersive virtual reality game that challenges you to think creatively and use your problem-solving skills to progress through increasingly challenging levels. With its unique gameplay mechanics and range of puzzles to solve, the game provides a satisfying and engaging experience for anyone looking for a fun and challenging VR gaming experience.",
